(Summary) Tj
T*
(Evolution is a valuable part of Biology. Students perform better when they understand) Tj
T*
(adaptation, variation, and natural selection, learn from examples such as explaining how) Tj
T*
(a useful trait becomes common, and deliberately avoid mistakes like thinking individuals) Tj
T*
(evolve during their lifetime. Regular practice built around adaptation and selection) Tj
T*
(reasoning makes the topic easier to remember and apply.) Tj
